Overview and modification¶

Some possible data modification:

Dummy Variables:    
    Gender: male==1 / female = 0
    Smoker: yes=1 / no=0

Categorical Variables: 
    Age: 
        <=18  : 0 
      18<x<30 : 1
         >30  : 2

    Region: 
        sw: 0
        se: 1
        nw: 2
        ne: 3
In [7]:
# Sex and smoker modifications

df['smoker'] = np.where(df['smoker']=='yes',1,0)
